@node USE "how to do it !"


			How do you use LHAtidy ?
			------------------------

	This is a complex command to use !

	Open a shell, go to the directory you wish to tidy up then type;

		LHAtidy  <filename.lha>

	Thats it, or you can use wild cards

		LHAtidy #?.lha


			    @{"Back to Main Menu"LINK MAIN}

